---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Projects
description: Independent work — Corrigibility, OpenSLM, Layer 8, the Indic Project, Moving Republic, and Swathanthra Malayalam Computing.
---
<article>
  <header>
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>
    <h1>Independent work, six lines.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Each runs on its own clock. None of them is the whole job.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <ul class="wi-list">
      {% for p in projects %}
        <li>
          <p class="name">{{ p.name }}</p>
          <div class="body">
            <p class="scope">{{ p.scope }}</p>
            <p class="desc"><strong>{{ p.role }}</strong> · {{ p.dates }}</p>
            <p class="link">
              <a href="{{ p.internalHref }}">More on this site →</a>{% if p.external %} · <a href="{{ p.external }}">{{ p.external | replace("https://", "") | replace("/", "") }}</a>{% endif %}
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
</article>
